{"tid":2099603,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屁股都有假，我屌！屁股移位　楊冪被質疑裝假籮","createTime":"2020-07-08T10:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T11:27:41.000Z","uid":23833,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"abb21b8a884d9cc2676f3517ab80f907613858cd","tid":2099603,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T10:43:06.000Z","msg":"<strong>蜜桃臀係流嘅？屁股移位　楊冪被質疑裝假籮<br />\r\n</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200708/bkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200708%2Fbkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001.html&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=a85ab416\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200708/bkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001.html</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200708/photo/bkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_01p.jpg?20200708133335\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200708%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20200708133335&h=cd268b19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n蜜桃臀是這樣煉成的？<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200708/photo/bkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_02b.jpg?20200708133335\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200708%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20200708133335&h=79dc7794&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n呢個樣嚇親唔少人！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200708/photo/bkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_03b.jpg?20200708133335\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200708%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20200708133335&h=f8f912b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n又平又扁？<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200708/photo/bkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_04b.jpg?20200708133335\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200708%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20200708133335&h=c9e125c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n影靚相就變翹臀？<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200708/photo/bkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_05b.jpg?20200708133335\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200708%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20200708133335&h=48c440e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n屁股位置有啲詭異！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200708/photo/bkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_06b.jpg?20200708133335\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200708%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20200708133335&h=10dae9cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n臀部疑似移位&hellip;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200708/photo/bkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_07b.jpg?20200708133335\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200708%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200708133255751-0708_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20200708133335&h=91ff8cec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n究竟真相係點？<br />\r\n<br />\r\n大陸女星楊冪早前面部意外崩壞照嚇驚網民，雖然佢之後嘅旗袍Look為佢扳回一城，點知櫈都未坐暖，又被網民質疑「裝假籮」！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n社交網流傳楊冪私下被粉絲影低嘅生活照，發覺佢個Pat Pat比較扁平，而出席公開活動時就有好曲線，名副其實嘅蜜桃臀！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n另外仲有從後台方向影佢背部嘅照片，見佢屁股位置有啲詭異，網民話疑似臀部「移位」，質疑佢平時出席公開場係裝咗假屁股！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n有網民就直言「女明星為了美也是拼了」、「知道有假胸原來還有假屁股」、「為了拍照效果好點沒甚麼很正常​​」，亦有人為楊冪平反，話只係影得衰啫！"},{"pid":"59c1e60a9cda7b7d698daf51ddcc32107460a2a7","tid":2099603,"uid":33643,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"repl